Enter adjacency matrix (0 if no edge):
0 2 0 6 0
2 0 3 8 5
0 3 0 0 7
6 8 0 0 9
0 5 7 9 0
Edge    Weight
0 - 1   2
1 - 2   3
0 - 3   6
